{"word":"Art","slug":"art","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Art</b> Primitive:<br/> - Invention of musical instruments and instruments of iron and copper<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=22'>Gen 4:22</a> <br/> - Carpentry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=6&verse=16'>Gen 6:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=31&verse=9'>Exo 31:9</a> <br/> - Of the:<br/> b Apothecary or perfumer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=25'>Exo 30:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=35'>Exo 30:35</a><br/> b Armorer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=12'>1Sa 8:12</a><br/> b Baker<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40&verse=1'>Gen 40:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=13'>1Sa 8:13</a><br/> b Barber<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=7&verse=20'>Isa 7:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=5&verse=1'>Eze 5:1</a><br/> b Brickmaker<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=11&verse=3'>Gen 11:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5&verse=8'>Exo 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5&verse=18'>Exo 5:18</a><br/> b Calker<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=9'>Eze 27:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=27'>Eze 27:27</a><br/> b Compounding confections<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=13'>1Sa 8:13</a><br/> b Gardener<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=29&verse=5'>Jer 29:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=15'>Joh 20:15</a><br/> b Goldsmith<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=40&vers